Officials say a furniture store caught alight earlier on Tuesday. CAPE TOWN - Firefighters are attending to a fire in Bellville. Officials say a furniture store caught alight earlier on Tuesday. Authorities are still on the scene. The city's fire and rescue services' Theo Layne said: “Currently, the fire is contained, no injuries have been reported and the cause of the fire is undetermined.” (Edited by Thapelo Lekabe)